{"word":"G647 - ἀποστάσιον - apostásion - ap-os-tas'-ee-on - Divorcement","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποστάσιον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>apostásion"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ap-os-tas'-ee-on"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Divorcement"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"தள்ளுதற்சீட்டு - பால் வேறுபாடு அல்லாத பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"divorce, repudiation, a bill of divorce"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Neuter of a (presumed) adjective from a derivative of <a href=\"#/G868 - ἀφίστημι - aphístēmi - af-is'-tay-mee/868\">G868</a>; properly something <i>separative</i>, that is, (specifically) <i>divorce:</i> - (writing of) divorcement."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}